      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "—So the Hebrew text of Chronicles spells the name, and the LXX. and all the other ancient versions both of Samuel and Chronicles have it so. But the Hebrew margin of Chronicles writes “Huram.”",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Messengers.—Ambassadors.",
