            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Timber of cedars.—Felled from the Lebanon, and sea-borne to Joppa (2 Chronicles 16).",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "Timber of cedars.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "—Felled from the Lebanon, and sea-borne to Joppa (2 Chronicles 16).",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "With masons and carpenters.—Literally, and craftsmen of walls, and craftsmen of timber. 2Samuel 5:11 has “craftsmen of wood, and craftsmen of stone of wall.”",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "With masons and carpenters.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "—Literally, and craftsmen of walls, and craftsmen of timber. ",
            "children": []
